name: Midwest Express - The Audiophiles
description: Midwest Express - The Audiophiles: Fresh Coast beats brought to you for your listening and recording pleasure.  This CD is collected beats from October of 2008 to April of 2009, which means you can still smell the that new album scent!

name: Midwest Express - ...And the Abandoned Factory
description: More beats from the Fresh Coast.  Midwest Express is series of beats made with a Sony program that I'm new at.  However, these beats are unlike anything I ever made before.  Don't believe me, listen to Umma al Jin at www.myspace.com/thequon for proof.  Album is available June 30th, 2009.

name: DJ Quon - On the House
description: DJ Quon - On the House: Listen to a musical slugfest of high bravado beats that will make your system bang and leave your ears ringing.  Recorded in 2005 shortly before fleeing the country, this album has the urgency and the brashness of a man on the run.

name: The Quon - 7 Months of Struggle
description: The Quon - Seven Months of Struggle - Maybe its because its been too long, but the Quon is kind of a forgotten artist these days.  Well all that is about to change on Sept. 30th.  Composed of all new beats by Midwest Express, this album is sure to be his most thought-provoking, personal and lyrically descriptive yet.  Be on the lookout late fall for this new album.  Be afraid, very afraid.

name: The Quon - DANK Remixes
description: The Quon - DANK Remixes : The Quon is betting you will enjoy the new and improved versions from the Dank EP!, HF S***, The Report and the Contraband Mixtape.  Each of these tracks has been recorded during 2009 and will be ready for 2010!  Think of the old tracks you love with full studio production, better vocals and hotter beats.  This is the 6 years of potential brought to fruition.  Release date: December 16th, 2009.
